<task id="changeoil" xml:lang="en-us">
<title>Changing the oil in your car</title>
<prolog><metadata></metadata></prolog>
<taskbody>
<context><p>Once every 6000 kilometers or three months, change the oil in
your car.  This 
will help keep the engine in good condition. </p><p>To change the oil:</p>
<p><table>
<tgroup cols="2">
    <colspec colname="aa" colwidth="3*"/>
    <colspec colname="bb" colwidth="2*"/>
    <thead>
    <row>
        <entry colname="aa">aa</entry>
        <entry colname="bb">bb</entry>
    </row>
</thead>
    
<tbody>
<row>
<entry colname="aa">aa</entry>
<entry colname="bb">bb</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</p></context>
<steps>
<step><cmd>Remove the old oil filter.</cmd></step>
<step><cmd>Drain the old oil.</cmd></step>
<step><cmd>Install a new oil filter and gasket.</cmd></step>
<step><cmd>Add new oil to the engine.</cmd></step>
<step><cmd>Check the air filter and replace or clean it.</cmd></step>
<step audience="abc"><cmd>Top up the windshield washer fluid.</cmd></step>
</steps>
</taskbody>
<related-links>
<link href="../concepts/oil.xml" format="dita" type="concept"><linktext>Oil</linktext>
</link>
<link href="../concepts/wwfluid.xml" format="dita" type="concept"><linktext>Windshield
washer fluid</linktext></link>
</related-links>
</task>
